OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lydon's wife dies from
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAlzheimer's at 80          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nora Forster, the wife of singer John  
OL,6, Lydon, has died five years after being 
OL,7, diagnosed with Alzheimer's disease.    
OL,9,FThe former Sex Pistols frontman was    
OL,10,Fmarried to the German publishing       
OL,11,Fheiress for 44 years. She was 80.      
OL,13,FIn recent years, he has spoken movingly
OL,14,Fabout becoming a devoted carer for     
OL,15,FForster as her illness took hold.      
OL,17,FHe also wrote a song for her which he  
OL,18,Ftried to enter on behalf of Ireland for
OL,19,Fthis year's Eurovision Song Contest,   
OL,20,Falthough it ultimately wasn't selected.
